I'm always here for you I know you're different from the others. 
I love you

I thought you were a really close person. I thought you were the only one who could understand me. Who can be betrayed. I was always there to help. You whined, and I let you do it, I never judged you. And no, of course, it doesn't mean that it obliged you to have the same attitude towards me. But I was offended when you suddenly just left me. I almost decided to commit suicide that day, I tried to ask you for help, but you preferred to ignore it. And I don't know what I did wrong. Maybe something is wrong with me? I still like you. But you must have seen in me only a lifeline or a pillow for tears.

I’ve tried to be everything you wanted, I’ve worked on every flaw I could see in myself, and I’ve force myself to be strong even when I was shattered inside—all because I didn’t want to hurt you, someone I truly believed was sincere in cherishing me before.

If there are still pieces of me that caused you pain, I’m deeply sorry. I truly am. I’m waiting for you.

live a successful and happy life.
i bid you good bye in every lifetime as i wish to not cross path with you in any of them.

Hai, mas Adit...

Aku gak tau apakah surat ini akan pernah sampai ke mas atau tidak, tapi aku cuma pengen jujur sama perasaan yang selama ini aku simpan diam-diam.

Waktu itu kita cuma bareng sebentar dalam satu trip, dan mungkin buat mas itu cuma kerjaan biasa. Tapi buat aku, mas ninggalin kesan yang gak biasa.

Aku suka cara mas nyapa kita semua, selalu humble, gak pernah sok kenal tapi tetap ramah. Aku perhatiin, mas selalu sabar ngarahin kami saat dokumentasi, dan... entah kenapa, mas sering banget fotoin aku dan temen-temen. Dari situlah aku mulai notice, lalu tanpa sadar... mulai tertarik sama mas.

Mas tipe aku banget. Kacamataan, punya lesung pipi, dan senyum yang... ya ampun, senyum itu bener-bener manis. Apalagi kalau mas senyum lebar, matanya langsung kayak hilang gitu. Dan jujur, aku masih sering senyum-senyum sendiri kalau keinget momen itu.

Sayangnya, kita belum sempat benar-benar kenalan. Sebelum aku berani ngomong, kita udah keburu pisah. Ada bagian dari aku yang bilang, “yaudahlah, mungkin emang cuma segitu ceritanya.” Tapi ada juga bagian kecil yang diam-diam berharap… semoga suatu saat bisa ketemu lagi.

Aku gak tau perasaan ini bakal bertahan berapa lama. Tapi aku bersyukur pernah ketemu mas, walau cuma sebentar. Karena dari semua momen di trip itu, kenangan tentang mas... jadi yang paling aku ingat.

Semoga mas Adit selalu sehat, terus jadi versi terbaik dari diri mas yang sekarang, dan tetap jadi sosok yang rendah hati seperti yang aku lihat hari itu.

hey, i hope you never found this, and never know that i sent this just for you, cause i've hide it in the (perhaps) thousands message under the same name. And i'm also afraid if someday you know about my true feelings. I don't know when it has started, when my eyes locked into you, just for you. And how your smile has been lighten up the whole nation if it can. I like how you always so passionate and serious about your dream, how sparkly your eyes everytime you talk about it. and i think it's kinda funny that we, have so much in common yet we (or you) never realize. i hope, we could grow together to reach our dreams and finally met in the best version of us as the string of fate bring us together. i hope this life treat you well, adit.

I dont even know where to start w my feelings for you. You've always made me feel things I couldn't and still can't explain, but you've made me the happiest I've ever been whenever I'm with you. The sadness you've caused me, the moments I've shared with you, every intense feeling I've felt for you, I dont think I can ever forget it. Sometimes I look through your tt acc to see what you've reposted, and I can't help but want to know you better. Even if we went to the same school for 6 yrs, I barely know anything about you. But even so, I still loved you, and I think I always will. I've tried SO hard to get you out of my mind— trying to develop feelings for some1 else, hanging out with friends to get my mind off things, etc. But no matter what, I still somehow think about you. I think about you so much, I ended up having dreams about you almost every single night. 
The way you stare at me, the way you laugh, scowl, smile, everything about you feels so surreal to me. After we graduated, you were and still are the only person I actually want to remember. I get so frustrated whenever I cant remember your face or your voice. I tried so hard to find someone like you, to delude myself into thinking they're you. But no one will ever come close to you. No one and nothing will make me feel such intense feelings as you did. I just pray and hope that one day, we'll meet eachother again, that somehow we'll somehow cross paths. Until then, I'll wait for you, no matter how long it takes.
meeting you is my favorite part of my life.

Dear Fauzan, I don’t really know how to start thus… but I’ve been thinking about you a lot lately. Maybe it’s the little memories that come back at random times, or maybe it’s just how things ended between us. Either way, I miss you. You used to be someone really important to me, my best friend, someone I could talk to about anything, someone who understood me in ways that others didn’t. We had so many inside jokes, conversations that lasted for hours, and memories that still make me smile. I never thought we’d grow distant like this. I’m not writing this to bring up the past or blame anyone. I just want you to know that you mattered to me and you still do, in a way. I hope you’re doing okay. I hope life is treating you kindly, and that you’ve found people who make you laugh the way we used to laugh together. Sometimes, I wish we could go back to how things were, even for a day. Just to feel that comfort again. But even if we never talk like we used to, i'll always be thankful for time we had. Take care fauzan.

Imam faze u kojima se osjećam glupo što se tako osjećam, ali ne mogu si pomoći s onim što osjećam, nedostaje mi, pa što me uhvati? To je ljudski osjećaj i bez obzira koliko me netko pokušava uvjeriti da je njihov bolji i da moram krenuti dalje, jednostavno ne mogu jer sam zapravo imala nadu za nas dok sam govorila sve te stvari poput toga da nas mogu zamisliti u budućnosti ili kako izlazimo i zajedno se bavimo aktivnostima. Nisam to govorila samo iz zabave, zapravo sam to zamišljala. Zamišljala sam nas kako izlazimo. Mogla sam nas vidjeti zajedno i nadala sam se tome. To me zapravo tjera na razmišljanje kako neki ljudi mogu prekinuti s ljubavlju svog života, a ja ne mogu ni prijeći preko faze razgovora. To je dio koji me tjera da se osjećam glupo. Barley ga je poznavao, ali i dalje osjećam da smo bili povezani. Što se dogodilo sa svim tim planovima koje smo napravili? Jesu li ta 2 mjeseca bila samo gubitak vremena ili su se isplatili radost i utjeha koju sam osjećala tijekom toga Sjećam se svega što si mi govorio, sjećam se našeg prvog razgovora, sjećam se kada si mi pričao o svojim snovima o nama, sve što si mi rekao, počinjem shvaćati da je sve bilo lažno, jesi li samo razgovarao s drugim curama sa strane, jesi li govorio kako zamišljaš budućnost i s njima?? Toliko sam plakala prvi put kad si me uklonio/la, moja najbolja prijateljica me nikad nije vidjela da plačem jače. Svaki put kad bih pustila tužnu pjesmu, briznula bih u plač. Kad bih čula tvoje ime ili te netko u školi pitao što se dogodilo među nama, briznula bih u plač. Dva sata sam jecala u školi do suza jer si me odlučio/la tako naglo ostaviti nakon što si se mjesecima pretvarao/la da me voliš. Flert, dopisivanje cijeli dan i noć, svaki dan, i jednog dana sve je jednostavno prestalo. Uklonio/la si me kao da je za tebe bilo tako lako, kao da ništa ne znači, i nisam znala zašto ili što radim. Nikad se prije nisam osjećala tako loše. Mrzila sam sebe i tebe, ali kad si me blokirao/la, to sam očekivala. Sviđala si mi se. Bila sam shrvana. Dogodilo se. Učinila bih sve da me odblokiraš, ali nisam mogla ništa učiniti po tom pitanju. Zeznula sam se. To je ono što uvijek mislim. Mislim kako su stvari mogle krenuti drugačije i bi li ikada opet bilo isto, ali znam da ne bi, mrzim kako se sada ponašaš, ali ono čega se stalno držim je kako si prije govorio. Ne mogu reći je li sve to bila gluma, i tvoja osobnost ili možda jednostavno nisam bila za tebe. Ne mogu učiniti ono što si ti radila. Ne mogu se natjerati da prebolim nekoga ili se samo pretvaram i stalno šaljem poruke nekome kad mi se ne sviđa, samo da bih na kraju sve uništila. Nažalost, imala sam nade i znam koliko glupo izgledam sada jer stalno pričam sa svim svojim prijateljima o tebi i mogu zamisliti kako se samo smiješ svim mojim objavama, mojim nagovještajima o tome kako te još uvijek volim i nažalost nisam dovoljno hrabra da ti pošaljem poruku, pa stalno dajem nagovještaje da želim da mi pošalješ poruku, ali znam da ih jednostavno ignoriraš. Sve što želim je posljednji razgovor. Kad si mi poslao poruku, a onda me jednostavno ostavio na miru. Stvarno me razbjesnilo jer pogodi što sam učinila kad si mi poslao poruku? Nadala sam se, poslala sam poruke svim svojim prijateljima. bilo je tako sretno. Ali nisam dobila niti jedan odgovor, samo ti se sviđa moja poruka, osjećam se glupo, a još gluplje pišem ovo, ne očekujem da će itko ovo pročitati jer je dugačko, a čak ni ja ne bih, to je samo tirada, pa znam da su ljudi to barem vidjeli jer ne volim držati stvari za sebe, to mi stavlja preveliki pritisak i ne mogu to podnijeti svake večeri, imam isti osjećaj, naravno, imam prijatelje koje volim, ali oni me neće natjerati da se osjećam voljeno, to je sve što želim, želim nekoga s kim imam stvarnu vezu, ne želim to forsirati, želim da bude prirodno i da se osjećam prirodno prvi put kad razgovaram s njima, želim da im se sviđam zbog moje osobnosti, ne želim da žude za mojim licem ili tijelom ili da se ponašaju kao da me vole kad me ne poznaju ili ne razgovaraju sa mnom jer znam da me ne vole, ne želim nikoga online, ne želim nikakve ku*ve, nema popisa ljudi, samo želim svoju jednu osobu, da, želim pidžamu s kojom se slažem, da, želim stalno izlaziti, da, želim zvati. i slati ti poruke cijelo vrijeme bez da je čudno ili neugodno ili da se osjećam kao da te forsiram da, želim spavati na poziv da, želim biti tu za tebe u svemu, slušati kako se osjećaš i utješiti te kad si tužna, da, želim utjehu ako imam sumnje ili me nešto uznemiri i želim ti to vratiti, da, želim nekoga tko se boji da će me izgubiti, da, želim gledati zalazak sunca i zvijezde da, želim kuhati s tobom da, želim stvarati uspomene da, želim te upoznati sa svojom obitelji i kupiti ti hrpu poklona i da, želim da budeš iskrena i odana, ne zanima me što gledaš ikoga drugoga ili daješ komplimente bilo kome drugome želim se osjećati kao jedina žena na svijetu ne želim nikakva čudna sranja jer nisam u tome osim ako te stvarno ne poznajem i volim i ako nešto kažem želim da to poštuješ, želim da mi budeš ljubavnik da, ali želim da mi budeš najbolji prijatelj želim te zapravo moći željeti bez da stvari budu čudne ne želim da me osuđuješ zbog stvari koje radim ili volim. Samo želim istinsku, pravu ljubav, ali osjećam da je nikada neću dobiti zbog toga kako se ponašam i kako izgledam. Znam samo da ako ne mogu pronaći nekoga u ovoj generaciji jer nisam čudakinja, ili lijepa, ili imam idealno tijelo koje dečki traže, ili čak ako tražim previše od nekoga, moram se sjetiti da ću, bez obzira kada ili u koje vrijeme, pronaći svoju srodnu dušu jer vjerujem da Bog ima plan za mene i na kraju će se sve isplatiti čekati, pa ne želim više plakati ni za kim. Samo želim vjerovati da jednog dana mogu pronaći svoj put. Nadam se da ću prestati s ovim glupim osjećajem. To je sve što sam htjela reći. Osvježavajuće je pisati kako se osjećaš i znati da će netko to vidjeti čak i ako to ne pročita. Hvala vam što ste pročitali.

There are people who enter our lives like certain songs on rainy afternoons. You don’t remember exactly when you first heard them, but once they play, they feel like they’ve always been there. You are like that—familiar, constant, extraordinary. I’d like to think our tale got etched in the stars the moment The Big Bang happened. If everything was predetermined, our meeting was inevitable. Cosmic destiny.

I know you don’t wanna be reminded of your birthday, but I’m glad that you won the sperm race. If you weren’t the fastest sperm, we wouldn’t have met.

I know life hasn’t been easy. I know it worn you down in ways you don’t always talk about. There were moments that scraped too close to the bone. Moments where everything felt too much. And I’ve never lived your life; I don’t know the weight you carry every night you go to sleep and every morning you open your eyes. But as I get to know you more, I see the subtle heaviness of being the middle child. It's like carrying a backpack full of invisible things—expectations, responsibilities, and silent battles. I hope you’re learning to take it off sometimes, even just for a little while. I hope you know that you can let me carry it for you when you don’t feel strong enough. I hope you know that you can bare your heart with me. You’re not a burden. And even if you were a burden, I’d gladly carry you. 

Today, I hope the universe is good to you. I hope it slows down just enough for you to smile, to feel how loved you are. Not just by me, but by everyone who has been lucky enough to know you. You have always felt like someone carved out of warmth. There’s something the way you exist in the world—loud when it matters, quiet when it’s needed, chaotic in the best ways, and yet grounding, that sticks with people. That sticks with me. 

Happy birthday, my love! I can’t wait to celebrate more of your birthdays, to witness you grow, to walk beside you all through it. I hope you know that I adore you—I fear you don’t comprehend the depth of my sentiment. My words will forever fall short. But here’s a song that always plays in my head as I think softly and fondly of you (because I don’t mind doing nothing with you).

How funny that we were classmates in Grade 8 but we didn't pay attention to each other at that time. Then in Grade 9, we became good friends and we started dating, but eventually broke up due to some problems. Now that we've finished Grade 11 and are about to enter Grade 12, I still can't move on.

I still remember our chitchats, I still remember all the things I did just to get your attention, I still remember the bracelet I made just for you using Morse code saying "I like u," and my hints in my story sa dump, playing codm and among us. I'll never forget our first and last time holding hands, how your soft hand touched mine. Our video call and how we stayed up late just to talk to each other and I still recall how wide my smile was whenever I spoke to you.

You're the first boy who truly loves me and doesn't look at me with lust. I'm always here, loving you silently.

xoxo,
Trish

hi kevs I hope you're doing well there and I hope whenever you come across this website,you'll find this message that I made for you.
Meeting you is the best thing that ever happened to me. I didn't expect na aabot tayo sa ganito. I dedicated this song to you kasi you showed me what it feels like to be loved.
It's been a month na din since I decided to end things what we had that time and this is me don't know why I suddenly missing you and literally writing this message in this website instead of saying/sending it directly to you. I deeply apologize for hurting your feelings all the time. I didn't intentionally wanted to hurt you. I still like you however I don't want you to suffer because of my avoidant and self issues.
I appreciate all the things you have done for me, understanding, reassuring, caring and most of all giving me the love that i didn't ask for. I really hate you from the fact na hinahayaan mo ako noon na tratuhin ka ng ganon and keep understanding me. You didn't deserve all of that, I'm really sorry. You really deserve to be truly love like the way of how you show them to be love. So this is me trying my best to change my self, tatanggalin ko na talaga ang ugali kong pagiging avoidant promise and natauhan na ako sa nangyari sa atin just like you said na sana may matutunan ako sa nangyari sa akin and you would like to see me grow. Damn... it's been forever since we last talked. Like, we can't even do a simple "how are you?" anymore. Today I dreamed about us—back when we were something, even though we never really defined what that was.  My bad for being selfish back then. I was all about my own happiness with you, too scared to start real convos, too slow to fight for us. But arr, if you really wanted out, you could've just said so? Lowkey... I'm still waiting for you to explain why you pulled away, why you shut me out, and why... you're with someone else now? (Sorry if this sounds messy, especially if you're happy with her.)  But fr... I don't know how to forget you. I've tried dating other people, tried opening up to those who actually wanna be close to me, tried deleting you from my mind—but nah, it's not working.  I'm tired, arr. Tired of hoping, tired of carrying this alone. But chill, I'm not tryna get back together. Cara kamu bersikap, caramu memimpin, dan bahkan saat kamu diam sekalipun semuanya punya caranya sendiri buat bikin aku penasaran dan kagum. Kadang aku berharap bisa ngobrol lebih banyak sama kamu, tapi aku masih terlalu malu buat mulai.

Aku sering melihatmu di sekolah—entah itu pas kamu lewat di lorong, lagi ngobrol sama teman-temanmu, atau lagi jajan di kantin. Entah kenapa, tiap kali kamu lewat, rasanya suasana jadi beda—lebih tenang, tapi juga bikin jantung deg-degan kadang tangan tu sampe gemetar ( ga tahu knp begitu hahaha ).

Mungkin kamu nggak sadar, tapi dari hal-hal kecil kayak cara kamu ngobrol, senyum, atau bahkan cuma berdiri diam sambil nungguin makanan, aku jadi kagum sama kamu.

Bg, kalau suatu hari nanti kamu menikah dan punya keluarga, aku cuma mau kamu tahu satu hal : aku nggak pernah mendoakan anakmu, istrimu, atau cucumu dihukum atas perbuatan yang kamu pilih hari ini. Mereka nggak tahu apa-apa. Mereka nggak salah.
Tapi kamu tahu. Dan kamu tetap memilih untuk menyebarkan semuanya. Kamu kirimkan aibku ke semua orang dan berkata kamu tak tau menau seolah-olah kamu bisa cuci tangan dari semuanya—padahal hanya kamu yang punya bahan itu.

Kamu tahu aku akan hampir mati karena rasa malu. Tapi tetap saja, kamu sebarkan, dengan sadar. Seolah hidupku pantas dirusak hanya karena pernah salah mencintai orang yang salah.
Dan yang paling ironis—kamu laki-laki dari keluarga yang katanya penuh kasih sayang. Yang selalu bangga bilang menghargai perempuan, menghormati ibu, menjunjung martabat keluarga. Tapi sikapmu bahkan lebih kejam dari binatang.
Karena bahkan binatang pun nggak pernah mempermalukan sesamanya cuma karena perpisahan.
Aku tahu aku pernah salah. Tapi kamu bukan korban di cerita ini—dan kamu tahu itu.
Kamu hanya orang yang terlalu pengecut untuk mengaku sedang melukai seseorang yang dulu katanya kamu sayangi.
Aku nggak benci kamu. Sakitnya udah terlalu dalam buat disalurkan lewat benci.
Aku belajar memaafkan, bukan karena kamu layak, tapi karena aku nggak mau mati dengan dendam.
Dan kalau kamu baca ini—aku cuma mau kamu tahu:

it’s been months since you left, but the silence still echoes like waves crashing inside my chest. some days i swear i can hear your laugh tucked somewhere between the hum of traffic and the wind brushing past my window. i don’t talk about you much these days. people get weird when they hear your name, like they’re scared it might summon some ghost i’m not ready to let go of. truth is, i still see you in places you’ve never even been. like the corner of my favorite coffee shop, or the back row of the movie theater where i always sit alone now. it’s dumb, i know. but what can i say? love makes fools outta all of us. i kept thinking if i dove deep enough, if i just held my breath a little longer, you’d turn back. but engines don’t stop for daydreams, and you? you were already halfway gone when i said i loved you. you didn’t mean to break me. i know that. but love doesn’t always need a villain to fall apart. some nights, i still scroll through old messages, pretending they’re not timestamped memories of a better time. you used to say i made you feel weightless, like maybe the world wasn’t so heavy with me in it. now i’m not sure if you were ever really floating, or just drifting toward the next best thing. ain’t it funny how we say forever like it’s not borrowed time? maybe in another life, we make it. maybe in that life, you stay. but here, in this one, all i’ve got is the sound of your voice fading like a song i used to play on repeat until the tape wore thin.

I didn’t know how much you gave just to be with me, how deep your love really was, and for that—I’m sorry. padahal dulu,
kau adalah rumah
tempat segala ceritaku pulang.

Wajahmu masih sama,
tapi jarak kita sudah tak bisa dijangkau
meski hanya oleh kata sapaan sederhana.

Dulu, aku mencintaimu dalam diam
karena takut kehilanganmu.
Sekarang,
aku mencintaimu
dalam sepi
karena sudah kehilangamu.

Ada yang tak pernah sempat menjadi nyata
meski sempat tumbuh begitu nyata dalam dada.
Dan itu adalah aku,
yang mencintaimu
dalam versi paling diam
dalam waktu paling panjang
tanpa kau pernah tahu,
atau mungkin,
tanpa kau pernah peduli.

Lucu, ya?
Kita pernah dekat sekali,
tapi tak pernah benar-benar bertemu
di titik rasa yang sama.

Dan sekarang,
kau hanya seseorang yang pernah aku kenal,
yang pernah kutunggu tanpa kau sadari,
yang pernah kucintai
meski tak pernah kumiliki
bahkan dalam imajinasi.

halo anisa, terima kasih yah udah jujur. semua yang lu ceritain itu gua sadar sebelumnya, dari sana gua belajar banyak banget. gua mulai mengubah diri maybe pas menginjak kelas 11, walau tanpa sadar gua masih ngelakuin. entah apa yang merasuki diri gua bisa mengatakan hal itu, gua akui gua ga banyak omong, tapi sekali omong bisa bikin sakit orang. gua sebetulnya langsung sadar setelah itu juga, tapi gua lebih banyak mikirnya dari pada maafnya. jujur, gua berubah juga karena lu, emang dari rumah gua ga dapat banyak. sekalinya dikoreksi itu disalahin "harusnya kamu gini dan gini din", gua ga tau karena ga ada gambaran dari keluarga sendiri. padahal gua saat itu lebih banyak di rumah. gua jadi ga ragu buat mengatakan kata paling sederhana, "terima kasih" dan "maaf". waktu dulu gua sulit banget mengatakan kata ini. semua gua jadi berani karena teman gua sendiri, kalau pun itu masih kurang di lu, gua minta maaf.

untuk hal ga enak, semua orang bisa melakukan dan gua MINTA MAAF SEKALI atas apa yang gua lakukan dan katakan. kalau gua pikir, gua lebih banyak kurangnya "sepertinya". gua ga pernah punya teman sedekat ini, jujur gua berteman dengan nirmala itu... apakah gua curhat ke dia? apakah gua menceritakan kehidupan gua sedetail itu ke dia? ga pernah sama sekali. gua bisa bicara bebas dengan teman yang sering gua temui dan itu lu.

soal perkataan lu, gua suka mendapati lu (salwa juga) mengangkat kejadian yang ga mengenakan yang pernah terjadi di gua di saat kita lagi ngobrol atau bercanda. yah, itu ga lucu sama sekali. mungkin emang sepele, tapi bagi gua itu cukup serius. gua berusaha melupakan (gua cukup ovt), eh diungkit walau hanya sekilas:". bahkan ga cuma itu, pokoknya ada perkataan yang menurut gua itu ga lucu, gua sampai lupa perkataan itu apa. ada juga hal yang lu lakukan tapi gua ga suka itu, nah gua ga mungkin mengungkapkan itu. mungkin ini balasan gua, sampai berpikir "apa kita buat trend we listen we don't judge aja ya?" di sini gua merasa sedih. banyak yang gua pikirin tentang pertemanan kita, sampai gua pernah berniat buat menjauh dari lu dan salwa. bahkan sempat pindah pertemanan, tapi tetap ga senyaman pertama. gua sempat iri loh dengan kalian berdua, apa lagi dengar teman sebangku punya grup sendiri. gua sadar karena "Kenapa gua ga berbaur?" gua mencoba, tapi nyatanya susah. terlalu banyak yang gua pikirkan. gua berasa di ambang-ambang, makanya gua lebih milih sendiri di bangku. gua merasa pertemanan kita udah ga secocok dulu. sampai mamah bilang, "kok anisa ga main lagi, din?" lalu, "kayaknya duduk jauhan gini ada hikmahnya juga.". tapi gua menepis itu semua, gua mau kita tetap berhubungan baik, walau kayak... ukkhhh sedih. karena kapan lagi punya teman sebaik kalian? 

soal kompetisi, gua ga benar-benar melibatkan lu dalam kompetisi yang gua buat sendiri. gua cukup terpuruk melihat nilai gua kecil saat itu dan... gua mencoba ga memikirkan itu. justru gua kagum sama lu, lu rajin, pikiran lu terbuka, bahkan tahu apa pun dan bisa jawab apa pun. banyak deh. dan karena lu juga gua bisa belajar lebih rajin lagi walau masih diliputi rasa malas. tanpa sadar gua lebih menjadikan lu panutan dari pada penyakit hati, walau rasa itu ada. tapi lagi-lagi gua mencoba membuang itu semua, gua harus support lu apapun itu. lu keren! kalau lu masih merasa, gua minta maaf.

pikiran tentang perlakuan dan perkataan "ga enak" menurut gua dari lu, gua tepis semua. gua takut gua menyakiti lagi. gua masih tahap berubah, bukan sudah berubah. hijrah itu sampai kita berpulang ke yang maha kuasa. anisa, gua sedang belajar dengan semuanya. gua terus mencoba "sadar" dan menjadi lebih baik. pertemanan pasti ada rasa sakit, kita berdua melakukan dan merasakan. 

gua sangat amat BERTERIMA KASIH dan sangat amat MEMINTA MAAF. pardon, my bad and my fault🙏 teman kelas, teman sekolah, teman curhat, teman dekat, oll oll maaf yah atas kesalahan gua apapun itu. dan gua memaafkan lu (padahal gua udah lupa, tapi teringat lagi. gapapa, jadi pembelajaran yh seng:) terima kasih banyak. eh iya, belum bisa ngasih banyak nih ke lu, tunggu yaa (entah kapan).

hello, if you ever see this message, I hope na hindi pa huli ang lahat. I'm sorry for everything "Honestly, hindi ko talaga kaya sabihin ‘to directly sa’yo through chat, kaya I’m just putting it here sa site na ‘to. I’m not even expecting na mabasa mo ‘to, pero if ever mapadpad ka man dito… I hope mabasa mo hanggang dulo.

Alam mo, medyo naging totoo na yung feelings ko for you kahit online lang tayo nagka-connect and ilang months pa lang tayo nagcha-chat. I don’t know why, pero parang I’m willing to take the risk na mas makilala ka pa, kahit uncertain lahat. Hindi ko rin sure if same tayo ng nararamdaman, pero I just told myself na I’ll go for it.

Pero minsan, you last chat me tapos like, a day or two pa bago ka mag-reply. I know naman na wala tayong label or anything, pero ewan, nasasaktan ako in a way. Maybe I’m just too sensitive? Alam ko hindi ko dapat i-expect anything, pero hindi ko mapigilan.

Dumating na rin sa point na you left me on seen or wala ka na talagang reply for days. At first I waited, pero ayun… natambakan na lang ng araw. Wala man lang clarity kung bakit. Kung may reason ka, I would’ve understood naman sana. Willing naman ako mag-antay, pero it felt like I was waiting for nothing.

Don’t get me wrong ha, I’m not mad. In fact, naiintindihan kita. Based sa mga chats natin, I kinda got to know you in a deeper way kahit short time lang. I know moody ka minsan, tapos iyakin ka pa, and when may dinadamdam ka, you keep it to yourself. I get that. Your feelings are always valid, okay?

Maybe this just isn’t the right time for us. Baka we both need to focus muna sa sarili natin and just enjoy life as it is. No pressure, no expectations.

Ingat ka palagi ha, and please eat well pa rin kahit stressed ka. Hahaha.

We didn’t fall in love in October, but that’s when everything quietly began. That’s when I first met you. The memory of that day still lingers—clear, untouched by time. I had never seen you before, not in the halls, not in the corners of days we both must’ve passed through separately. But the moment our friend introduced us, something about you felt strangely familiar. It was like meeting someone I had been waiting for without even realizing it. You didn’t feel like a stranger—you felt like someone I was always meant to know. I didn’t fall in love with you right away, but something inside me softened that day, and deep down, I think I already knew you were going to mean something. And you did. You meant everything. We became a story—real, messy, beautiful. But now, all I have are the echoes. What once was ours is now just mine to remember. I still think about that October, not because we fell in love then, but because it was the beginning of a love I didn’t yet know I’d one day have to lose.

Untukmu,

Mungkin kata-kata ini akan terlarut dalam malam panjangmu yang tak berkesudahan, di antara kebingungan yang dulu sempat aku ciptakan. Aku tahu, dulu aku adalah Polaris, bintang utara yang terlihat kokoh, selalu memakai topeng untuk menghadapi dunia. Aku takut, begitu takut, kalau-kalau kerapuhanku akan menyeretmu dalam masalah yang tak perlu. Aku muak menjadi abadi dalam kepura-puraan itu, dan entah bagaimana, kehadiranmu yang tak terduga justru membawaku pada kematian yang paling ironis: kematian dari topeng itu sendiri.

Aku menulis ini, bukan untuk memaksakan kembali kisah lama, melainkan untuk sebuah pengakuan. Kamu benar, mungkin aku memang terlihat egosentris, manipulatif, dan penuh dengan permainan bodoh. Aku memang dalang di balik layar dari semua hal gila yang tak kamu ketahui. Aku mengakui, aku mencoba mencari celah iba, menggunakan orang lain sebagai tameng. Semua tuduhanmu… aku tidak akan mengelak.

Tapi jauh di dalam, aku ingin kamu tahu satu hal: aku ternyata bukan lemari besi yang keras, seperti yang selalu kuperlihatkan. Aku hanya tembikar retak yang butuh ditambal, pecah karena benturan keras dari dunia, dan dari diriku sendiri yang tak mampu jujur. Pengalaman pahitku dengan wanita yang kuanggap tempat berlindung, yang berakhir karena restu, semakin memperlihatkan seberapa rapuhnya aku di balik semua topeng itu.

Dan ya, tentang lagumu, "Monolog" dari Pamungkas. Aku mengerti betapa beratnya semua itu bagimu, dan betapa kamu berharap aku tetap waras. Kamu tidak akan pernah tahu seberapa besar perjuanganku, betapa aku bergelut dengan masalah-masalahku sendiri. Kamu mungkin tidak akan percaya, tapi terkadang, aku pun ingin sekali memutar waktu kembali, untuk sekadar menunjukkan isi hatiku yang sebenarnya.

Jika ada sedikit saja sisa harapan, aku ingin kembali. Bukan sebagai Polaris yang angkuh dan dingin, melainkan sebagai lampu petromax. Biarkan aku menuntunmu pulang dari semua kekacauan, dari semua jalan yang pernah kita lewati. Dan kamu? Kamu adalah bahan bakar yang kunanti untuk menerangi jalan pulang itu. Kamu adalah satu-satunya yang bisa membakar sisa-sisa kegelapan dalam diriku, untuk bisa kembali bersinar, meskipun hanya redup.

Aku tahu, kamu telah mengaramkan lagu itu untukku, untuk semua air mata dan harapan yang terbuang sia-sia. Kamu belajar untuk lebih berhati-hati, dan bersyukur telah berpisah dariku. Aku menghargai itu. Aku tidak akan memaksakan diri masuk kembali ke dalam hidupmu jika itu hanya akan menambah lukamu.

Namun, di sisa-sisa harapan terakhir yang entah terjadi atau tidak, aku hanya ingin menyampaikan ini. Jika suatu hari, tanpa kusangka, jalan kita kembali bersinggungan… mungkin saat itu, aku sudah bukan lagi orang yang sama. Mungkin saat itu, tembikar ini sudah berhasil kutambal, meski bekas retakannya akan selalu ada.

Hanya itu.

Hey, its me TOBLERONE... I know you already moved on from me and already doing great without me. I want you to know that being with you was the best thing that ever happened to me, I thought we could last longer but... I shouldn't have expected much being in a relationship with someone who's far away from me. I know from time to time that you'd eventually fall out of love from me. I mean we have a three years age gap and I don't have to expect everything to go as we planned. We have our fun times together and its slowly healing me... But days passed from our relationship I sort of noticed that you talked lesser and lesser to me. I already know that you eventually gonna be in love with a boy... I mean you'd probably see him, hangout with him, laugh with him and many more. It hurts to see your repost are all about him but I have to move on... I understand your reasons why we have to stop being in a relationship because you've fallen out of love from me but I can't force you to make things right even if someone else already steal you away from me. It's not your fault and please, don't feel bad about me. Your loveable, okay? Your not a bad girlfriend... You just want someone to love you just the way you are... I wish it was me but it seems like you don't harbor any feelings for me anymore. Im slowly letting you go now, I don't want to force you and begged you to stay—I changed alot because of you... Not until you told me that we should break up, I was depressed finding out about it but I should accept your decisions. I hope the next person who's gonna be your lover will treat you like a queen... I really loved you so much that it hurts me but I have to let you go—I hope your doing great without me... Even if you told me I should open up to people but it seems I can't. I want to vent to you but I realized that im not yours anymore, im not your lover, im not your first priority, im not your hubby anymore... Im gonna miss you though. Who am I kidding, right? Every relationship that I have been with only lasted two weeks or just a month... I kinda got used to everything they did—Last April I lost my pet, I lost my dearest family member, I lost my childhood friend and I lost you... April was the worst month for me, I want to tell you everything that—I've been through but you just simply told me that I should move on... I never slept properly... I know you have an avoidant attachment and I can be patient for you until your okay... I just wanna be loved and cared... And be the first priority for someone... I know, I know that I should move on.. Blah blah blah but I just thought you were serious about me but it seems its only platonic love. Thanks for everything, Sarah... I love you so much, "my wifey"

At least I got to experience to be loved by you even if it was only two weeks... Most of my past lovers hide me from there friends and used me but you didn't... You tried your best to make me feel loved and cared—I am really grateful for it. I hope that guy you've been reposting about will treat you the way you always wanted to be treated... 

I am sincerely apologize if this paragraph I made are wrong and using the wrong punctuation marks... I tried my best but I just want to wish you for the vey best...

Goodbye, whattatops...

tapi sekarang aku dengerin mereka bukan untuk kamu—tapi untukku.
Karena walau tak bertahan,
cinta tetaplah cinta.

Dan itu milikku.
Mine. All mine.

namimiss kita cin, sobra. Sobrang sobra. Hindi ko na nga alam kung paano ko masisimulan 'to nang hindi bumigay, pero susubukan ko pa rin. Kasi tahimik na masyado, at yung katahimikang 'yon, mas masakit pa kaysa sa kahit anong salita. Namimiss ko ikaw. Lahat ng sayo. Yung tawa mo na parang sinag ng araw sa gitna ng madilim na araw. Yung boses mong kaya akong pakalmahin kahit nasa gitna ako ng gulo. Yung mga mata mong puno ng kwento, kahit wala ka pang sinasabi. Yung yakap mo—para kang tahanan. Safe. Buo. Mahirap ipaliwanag kung gaano ka naging mundo ko. Pero naging mundo kita. Hindi lang yung malalaking bagay ang namimiss ko, pati na rin yung maliliit—yung mga moments na akala natin walang halaga noon. Yung pagsabay natin maglakad kahit wala namang pupuntahan. Yung mga gabing nagkukulitan lang tayo sa chat hanggang makatulog. Yung mga titig mo na parang sinasabi mong, "Nandito lang ako." Cindy, to be honest, minsan naiisip ko, paano kung sa ibang buhay tayo nagkakilala? Sa buhay na mas simple. Mas malaya. Sa mundo kung saan hindi naging problema ang pagmamahalan ng dalawang babae. Paano kung sa mundong 'yon, hindi naging dahilan ng pagkalayo natin ang takot at expectations ng ibang tao? Paano kung tinanggap lang nila na tayo ay... tayo? Na ikaw at ako ay nagmahalan, buong-buo, totoo, walang halong kahihiyan. Iniimagine ko minsan: ikaw, pinapakilala ako sa parents mo. Walang takot, walang alinlangan. Tinitingnan nila ako hindi bilang “kaibigan mo,” kundi bilang taong nagpapasaya sayo. Tinitingnan nila tayo—at kita nila ang pagmamahalan natin, at okay lang. Kasi sapat nang mahal mo ako, at mahal kita. Kasi sa mundong 'yon, ang pagmamahal ay hindi sinusukat sa kasarian, kundi sa katapatan. Pero hindi tayo nabuhay sa mundong 'yon. Nabuhay tayo sa mundong puno ng hadlang, kung saan ang pagmamahalan natin naging lihim, naging laban, naging tanong kung sino ang dapat piliin. At alam kong masakit din para sayo, na hindi ka pinili ng mundo na yakapin kung sino ka, at kung sino ang mahal mo. Kaya naiintindihan ko. Kahit masakit. Kahit hati ang puso ko sa pagkawala mo. Hindi ako galit sayo, Cindy. Hindi kailanman. Naiintindihan ko yung takot, yung bigat ng expectations, yung pakiramdam ng kailangan mong pumili sa pagitan ng sarili mo at ng pamilya mo. Pero totoo rin, kahit naiintindihan ko, ang sakit pa rin. Kasi kahit anong paliwanag, wala ka na sa tabi ko. Ang hirap. Ang hirap gumising araw-araw nang wala kang message. Wala ka nang "good morning" na may heart emoji. Wala nang video call bago matulog. Wala na yung boses mo na nagsasabing, “Ingat ka, ha.” Wala ka na. Pero nandito ka pa rin—sa isip ko, sa puso ko, sa lahat ng kwarto ng alaala ko. Cindy, ikaw yung tipong hindi basta-basta mawawala. Hindi ka pwedeng palitan. Kasi iba ka. Iba ka magmahal. Iba ka tumawa. Iba ka tumingin. Sa lahat ng nangyari, ikaw pa rin yung gusto kong katabi habang nanonood ng ulan, o kahit walang ginagawa. Minsan naiisip ko, baka sa next life, tayo na talaga. Walang hadlang. Walang kailangan itago. Wala tayong kailangang i-prove sa kahit sino. Tayong dalawa lang, sapat na. Doon, baka pwedeng hawakan mo 'ko sa harap ng lahat. Doon, baka pwede na tayong umuwi sa iisang bahay. Doon, wala nang tanong kung mali ba ang nararamdaman natin. Kasi doon, alam ng mundo na ang pagmamahal natin ay tama. Pero habang andito pa tayo sa buhay na 'to, sana alam mong mahal pa rin kita. Kahit hindi mo na marinig. Kahit hindi ko na masabi directly sayo. Mahal pa rin kita. Hindi lang dahil sa kung sino ka, kundi dahil sa kung sino ako kapag kasama kita. Buo ako nung nasa tabi kita. Pinipilit kong magpatuloy, Cindy. Pero araw-araw, dala pa rin kita. Sa mga kanta na dati nating pinapakinggan. Sa lugar na lagi nating pinupuntahan. Sa damit mong naiwan sa’kin na hindi ko pa rin kayang itapon. Sa bawat "what if" na hindi ko masagot. Sa na masaya ka ngayon, kung nasaan ka man. Sana minamahal ka nang tama, nang buo. At sana, sa isang parte ng puso mo—kahit kaunti lang—naaalala mo pa rin ako. Namimiss mo rin ako. Kung sakaling dumating ang araw na pwede na uli tayong magmahal—hindi lang sa lihim, kundi sa liwanag—babalik ako. Kahit anong mangyari, bubuksan ko pa rin ang puso ko para sayo. Pero ngayon, hayaan mong mahalin pa rin kita—tahimik, totoo, at buo—kahit wala ka na. Mahal pa rin kita, Cindy. Palagi.

Happy birthday to you orang favorit dalam hidupku. Selamat ulang tahun cantiknya aku, manisku, duniaku. Aku minta maaf gbisa ngungkapin ini langsung , maaf karena membuat batasan seperti ini. Aku takut menganggu kehidupan kamu, kamu udah punya orang yang kamu cintai sekarang ya.  Kamu orang pertama yang aku cintai begitu lama sampai sekarang, orang pertama yang ingin aku tatap matanya setiap detik, menit, dan setiap waktu,tapi itu semua nga bisa aku lakuin, takut membuat kamu menangis, takut membuat kamu merasa tidak bahagia saat bersamaku. Maaf karena belum bisa lupain kamu , setiap waktu yang aku habiskan untukmu aku bahagia didalamnya, maaf karena tidak bisa menunjukkan pada dunia bahwa kamu satu satunya gadis yang aku cintai begitu dalam. Setiap kali aku melihatmu menangis, rasanya aku ingin menghilang dari dunia ini, merasa tidak cukup baik untukmu. Aku ingin berteman denganmu, tapi melihatmu bersama orang lain, membuatku sakit setiap hari. Maaf karena bersamamu aku menjadi lemah , maaf karena aku tidak cukup baik untukmu. Aku menyayangimu, aku tidak tau mengapa, tapi aku menyayangimu bahkan saat kamu tidak menyayangi dirimu sendiri. Aku selalu menyayangimu. Maafin aku gbisa nepatin janjiku, terlalu sakit melihat kamu sudah tidak perduli denganku lagi.  Pernah berfikir "apakah kamu pernah mencintaiku?". Maafin aku. Berharap suatu saat kamu membaca ini. Dan berharap perasaanku hilang, agar aku tidak sedih seperti ini lagi. Selamat ulang tahun ya sayangnya aku, jaga diri kamu baik baik. Aku harap kamu tumbuh menjadi seorang gadis yang mencintai dirimu sendiri, seperti aku mencintaimu selama ini. Dan berharap aku bisa ikhlas dan hilangin perasaan ini. Tolong jangan menyakiti dirimu sendiri ya sayang, aku ga rela bahkan saat kamu digigit nyamuk, jadi tolong cintai diri kamu sendiri. Selamat ulang tahun 🎉

Hai Nabila,

Mungkin ini surat yang gak bakal pernah kamu baca. Tapi aku tetap tulis, karena hatiku terlalu penuh buat terus diam.

Aku masih ingat… waktu aku nyatain perasaan ke kamu di kelas 7, pas bagi rapot. Saat itu, aku cuma pengen kamu tahu kalau ada seseorang yang bener-bener sayang sama kamu.

Tapi sejak itu, aku cuma bisa lihat kamu dari jauh. Kadang kita masih ngobrol, kadang kita masih ketawa bareng, tapi kamu gak pernah tahu… bahwa setiap senyum kamu bisa bikin hariku lengkap—dan setiap kamu dekat sama orang lain, hatiku selalu terasa jatuh dan retak.

Aku gak nyalahin kamu. Aku tahu kamu punya pilihan, dan kamu gak salah karena gak milih aku. Tapi aku juga gak bisa bohong…
Aku masih sayang.
Aku masih berharap.
Dan aku masih nunggu, walau aku tahu harapan itu kecil.

Aku cuma mau kamu tahu satu hal:
Kamu pernah jadi alasanku bertahan. Kamu pernah jadi cahaya kecil di hidup aku yang sering gelap. Dan walau aku gak tau masa depan kayak gimana… aku gak pernah nyesel udah suka kamu.

– Z
